reviewText:
Greetings;

Going in, I expected that it was just another obscure title, something translated from a Japanese adult anime that just happened to come out. Sort of thing you see if you only ever really bother to check in and see whats out every few months. What I tend to do myself. Unfortunatly, wasn't even that so much. Granting not bad, but it was all just a lot of scenes from existing movies, there is another series like that I recall...All Sex Hentai, of which there are some three or so, I believe. Not sure why this wasn't just called the fourth or something instead. But in either case. On a lesser note, the box indicates that it is in English, while a good portion of it was english dubbed, some of it was in Japanese. Menu lets you skip to scenes, see trailers, play the 'video' and skip to what some would consider...The focal point of each scene.

Thank you and take care...
